const content = `<main>
    <section class="booking-hero"><div class="shell"><nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="m6 3 5 5-5 5"></path></svg><span>Book a clean</span></nav><div class="hero-grid"><div class="hero-copy"><div class="kicker">Online booking</div><h1>Book a clean,<br><em>get your week back.</em></h1><p>Easily book vetted, fully insured professional house cleaners across Melbourne with no lock-in contracts. Simply use our special code FIRST15 for 15% off your first eligible professional cleaning service today.</p></div><div class="hero-reassurance"><div class="reassurance-row"><i><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M7 11V8a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3M5 11h14v10H5z"></path></svg></i><div><strong>Secure checkout</strong><span>Protected online payment</span></div></div><div class="reassurance-row"><i><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 5h16v14H4zM4 8l8 6 8-6"></path></svg></i><div><strong>Email confirmation</strong><span>Sent once your cleaner is assigned</span></div></div><div class="reassurance-row"><i><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M12 3 4 6v6c0 5 3.3 8 8 9 4.7-1 8-4 8-9V6l-8-3ZM8 12l2.5 2.5L16 9"></path></svg></i><div><strong>Insured cleaners</strong><span>Professional home care</span></div></div></div></div></div></section>

    <div class="steps-band"><div class="steps shell reveal" aria-label="Booking steps"><div class="step"><span class="step-num">01</span><div><strong>Choose your service</strong><span>Home size and clean type</span></div><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M6 4l6 6-6 6"></path></svg></div><div class="step"><span class="step-num">02</span><div><strong>Add the details</strong><span>Frequency and extras</span></div><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M6 4l6 6-6 6"></path></svg></div><div class="step"><span class="step-num">03</span><div><strong>Pick a date</strong><span>Preferred day and time</span></div><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M6 4l6 6-6 6"></path></svg></div><div class="step"><span class="step-num">04</span><div><strong>Complete booking</strong><span>Contact and payment details</span></div><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M6 4l6 6-6 6"></path></svg></div></div></div>

    <section class="booking-section" id="booking"><div class="booking-layout shell">
      <div><div class="frame-card reveal"><div class="frame-card-head"><div class="frame-card-title"><span class="frame-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M5 4h14v16H5zM8 2v4M16 2v4M5 9h14M8 13h3M13 13h3M8 17h3"></path></svg></span><div><h2>Build your booking</h2><p>Complete each step below. Your progress stays inside the booking form.</p></div></div><span class="secure-label"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M7 11V8a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3M5 11h14v10H5z"></path></svg>Secure form</span></div><div class="frame-notice"><p><strong>The form may take a few seconds to load.</strong> Please keep this page open while completing your booking.</p><a class="text-link" href="https://mah.bookingkoala.com/booknow/home_cleaning" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open separately <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M7 4h9v9M16 4 8 12M4 7v9h9"></path></svg></a></div>
        <!-- Future integration boundary: replace the iframe inside bookingAppMount with the native booking application. -->
        <div class="booking-frame-wrap" id="bookingAppMount" data-booking-mode="iframe" data-future-component="native-booking-app"><div class="frame-loader" id="frameLoader"><div class="loader-inner"><span class="loader-ring"></span><p>Loading the booking form...</p></div></div><iframe class="booking-frame" id="bookingFrame" title="Maid At Home secure booking form" data-src="https://mah.bookingkoala.com/booknow/home_cleaning?embed=true&bar=false&banner=false" allow="payment; clipboard-write" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><div class="frame-fallback"><p>If the form does not display correctly in your browser, you can continue securely in a new tab.</p><a class="text-link" href="https://mah.bookingkoala.com/booknow/home_cleaning" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open booking form <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M7 4h9v9M16 4 8 12M4 7v9h9"></path></svg></a></div></div>
        </div>

      <aside class="booking-sidebar" aria-label="Booking help"><section class="side-card reveal"><h2>Before booking</h2><p>Having these details ready makes the booking quicker.</p><ul class="prep-list"><li><b>1</b><div><strong>Your suburb and address</strong><span>Used to confirm the service area and route.</span></div></li><li><b>2</b><div><strong>Home size and condition</strong><span>Bedrooms, bathrooms and the right service level.</span></div></li><li><b>3</b><div><strong>Preferred date</strong><span>Bookings need at least 24 hours' notice.</span></div></li><li><b>4</b><div><strong>Access and pets</strong><span>Share anything the cleaner should know.</span></div></li></ul></section>
        <section class="side-card payment reveal"><div class="payment-row"><span class="payment-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M3 6h18v12H3zM3 10h18M7 15h4"></path></svg></span><div><h3>Payment made simple</h3><p>Your card secures the booking. A temporary hold is generally placed 48 hours before the service and the final amount is charged after the clean.</p></div></div></section>
        <section class="side-card help-card reveal"><div class="whatsapp-row"><span class="whatsapp-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M20 11.5a8 8 0 0 1-11.8 7L4 20l1.5-4A8 8 0 1 1 20 11.5ZM8.5 9.5c1 2.2 2.1 3.3 4.3 4.3"></path></svg></span><div><strong>Need help choosing?</strong><span>Chat with our team on WhatsApp.</span></div></div><a class="button beige" href="/contact#whatsapp">Ask us first <i><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></i></a><div class="mini-policy"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M12 3 4 6v6c0 5 3.3 8 8 9 4.7-1 8-4 8-9V6l-8-3"></path></svg><span>If something agreed was missed, let us know within 24 hours so we can coordinate the right follow-up.</span></div></section>
      </aside>
    </div></section>

    <section class="section faq-section" id="faqs"><div class="faq-layout shell"><div class="faq-intro reveal"><div class="kicker">Before you book</div><h2>Booking questions.</h2><p>Clear answers about availability, payment and what happens after you submit the form.</p><a class="text-link" href="/faqs">Explore all FAQs <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></a></div><div class="faq-list reveal">
      <article class="faq-item open"><h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="true">Is my booking confirmed immediately?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>We receive your booking immediately, but the cleaner assignment is confirmed separately. We email you once a suitable cleaner or team has been organised for the date.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">How far in advance should I book?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>The booking system requires at least 24 hours' notice. For preferred times, larger homes, End of Lease Cleaning or carpet steam cleaning, booking earlier gives us more options.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">When will my card be charged?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>Your card secures the booking. A temporary authorisation is generally placed 48 hours before the service, or sooner for short-notice bookings. The final charge is processed after the clean.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">Do recurring savings apply to the first clean?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>The first service is charged at the normal one-off rate. Eligible savings begin from the second recurring Standard or Deep Clean: 10% weekly or fortnightly, and 5% every three or four weeks.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">Can I change my booking afterwards?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>Contact us as early as possible if something changes. Changes are subject to availability, and cancellation or rescheduling fees may apply when less than 24 hours' notice is provided.</p></div></div></article>
      </div></div></section>

    <section class="support-strip"><div class="support-inner shell reveal"><div class="support-copy"><i><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 5h16v12H8l-4 3V5ZM8 9h8M8 13h5"></path></svg></i><div><strong>Still unsure before booking?</strong><span>Tell us your suburb, home size and what you need. We will point you in the right direction.</span></div></div><div class="support-actions"><a class="button blue" href="/contact">Contact our team <i><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></i></a></div></div></section>
  </main>`;
